name: VisakhapatnamGuide
0:
”Alexa, Open Vizag guide and tell me a good attraction”
”Alexa, launch Vizag guide. and tell me the local news”
”Alexa, open Vizag guide and give me the top five”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: vizag guide
des:
One stop guide to all the fun and attractions in Visakhaptnam. This guide includes top 5 attractions, local news (data provided by New York Times) and other places such as parks, muesums with lots of learning and fun for kids and adults alike. You can also find the contact e-mail and phone numbers on the Alexa app on your devices - app on your smartphones or on your FireTV screen.
No need of troubles looking for a tour guide. All you need to do is ask Alexa what to lookout for and where to hangout.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
